PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of a number of tracts of land in the Yukon Territory, until March 31, 2002, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order (Liard First Nation, Y.T.), made by Order in Council P.C. 1996-1871.

precis:
Enactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN
LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) -  which
(a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of a number of tracts of land
in the Yukon Territory, until March 31, 2002, and (b) repeals the
Withdrawal from Disposal Order (Liard First Nation, Y.T.), made by Order
in Council P.C. 1996-1871.
